## Recent Developments
* In March 2023, Itron, Inc. signed a contract with Duquesne Light Company (DLC) to improve operational efficiency, update infrastructure, and enable smart city applications.
* In January 2023, YEELIGHT, a smart lighting manufacturer unveiled a new range of products including the Cube Smart Lamp, an Automatic Curtain Opener, and a Smart Scene Panel.

